<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>JAMJAM</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #FBCE26;
      color: #2C3E50;
    }
    nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      background-color: rgb(5 18 100);
    }
    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .logo img {
      height: 40px;
      object-fit: contain;
    }
    .login-btn {
      color: white;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #0056B3;
      border-radius: 25px;
      transition: background 0.3s;
    }
    .login-btn:hover {
      background-color: #003F80;
    }
    header {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #002B5C, #0056B3);
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 70px 20px;
    }
    header h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin: 0;
    }
    header p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .nav-center {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .nav-center a {
      text-decoration: none;
      background-color: #0056B3;
      color: white;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      transition: background 0.3s;
    }
    .nav-center a:hover {
      background-color: #003F80;
    }
    .section {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }
    .section h2 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: #1A2A3A;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .features {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 24px;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .feature {
      background: white;
      padding: 24px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
      flex: 1 1 300px;
    }
    .feature:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px);
    }
    .feature h3 {
      color: #007BFF;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .feature ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .feature ul li {
      padding: 8px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #F0F0F0;
    }
    .cta-buttons {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
    .cta-buttons a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 0 12px;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      background-color: #28A745;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      border-radius: 30px;
      transition: background 0.3s ease;
    }
    .cta-buttons a:hover {
      background-color: #218838;
    }
    footer {
      background-color: #1A2A3A;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav>
    <div class="logo">
      <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="JAMJAM Logo" />
    </div>
    <a class="login-btn" href="/buses/profile/"> Dashboard</a>
  </nav>
  <header>
    <h1>üöåJAMJAM</h1>
    <p>Making sure you are never late to important places ‚ò∫Ô∏è</p>
  </header>
  <section class="section">
    <h2>About the App</h2>
    <p style="text-align: center; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
     JAMJAM provides real-time bus schedules, route information, and timely alerts‚Äîmaking travel easier, smarter, and more reliable üíô
    </p>
  </section>
  <div class="nav-center">
    <a href="#">Find Routes</a>
  </div>
  <section class="section">
    <h2>Key Features</h2>
    <div class="features">
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>For Users</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Route Search</li>
          <li>Departure Alerts</li>
          <li>Fare Information</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>For Admin</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Alert & Notification Control</li>
          <li>User Management</li>
          <li>Route & Schedule Management</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section">
    <h2>Get Started</h2>
    <p style="text-align: center;">Join thousands of smart commuters with JAMJAM.</p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="#">Download App</a>
      <a href="#">Signup</a>
    </div>
  </section>
  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 JAMJAM | Contact | Terms | Privacy</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>


